{"tid":379040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人的悼念","createTime":"2017-08-29T03:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T03:00:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59b17fa69bee83f88e7d7ba5366b18e88dcf0f17","tid":379040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135760&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135760%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&d=CBxb65HEqgX8oStXjL8iVMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=aadee92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135760%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&h=8b72a0a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135760&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829</a><br />\n<br />\n點點光悼10死難者<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n        <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170829/large/29la4p11.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170829%2Flarge%2F29la4p11.jpg%20&h=5fa6ad67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是一個人的悼念。澳門警方這陣子不接受公眾活動申請，昨晚在新馬路噴水池，27歲女子灣灣在腰側掛一支小電筒，隱隱透光（圖），「澳門啲人一直選擇死忍，但點忍都好，10個人命&hellip;&hellip;點解一個防難、防災措施都做唔到？」<br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t侵犯政府威信可囚兩年<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t派飯餐廳老闆：澳門人堅毅少抱怨<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t吹歪20公里變澳門受災香港下次有無咁好彩？<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t指用微信傳假災情　澳門拘73歲兄68歲妹廉政專員查前氣象局長管理失當<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"11387c3b4cd8fe2a747ea0311ee8bb0e148048d2","tid":379040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}